works.description: While you could have Sir Richard Branson as your flight attendant for just £4,500, you’ll have to shell out, if interested, a whopping $650,000 to grab an opportunity to shave Branson’s legs. Lately, we told you about the hilarious move, in which British billionaire Sir Richard Branson has to dress and serve as a flight attendant on Malaysian budget carrier AirAsia on May 1 after he lost a Grand Prix bet with Tony Fernandes last November.
